  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Effect of AVE0657 in Cheynes-Stokes Breathing Syndrome Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Study Evaluating the Safety and Activity of Four Escalating Single Doses of AVE0657 in Congestive Heart Failure Patients Presenting as Cheyne-Stokes Breathing Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
